md:
giải nghĩa từ "edm" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

edm /ˈɛdɪm/ (noun)

* Meaning: Electronic Dance Music (nhạc điện tử nhảy)
* Example: The club was playing EDM music all night.
* Related words: DJ, club, party, rave, techno, trance.

edm (abbreviation)

* Meaning: Enterprise Data Management (quản lý dữ liệu doanh nghiệp)
* Example: The company implemented an EDM system to improve data quality.
* Related words: data, management, enterprise, IT, software.

edm (abbreviation)

* Meaning: Electrical Discharge Machining (gia công bằng điện phóng)
* Example: The manufacturer used EDM to create complex metal parts.
* Related words: machining, manufacturing, engineering, technology.

Note: EDM can have different meanings depending on the context. The above explanations are just a few examples of its usage.
